#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Handling"
msgstr "Ravnanje z arhivom"

#. Tag: primary
#: archives.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archives"
msgstr "Arhivi"

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing Archives"
msgstr "Brskanje po arhivih"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtual file systems (VFS)</link> allows you to "
"browse archives as if it was a folder. Currently &krusader; supports the "
"following archives types: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, "
"tar, xz, zip, and 7-zip and supports the following passworded archives: arj, "
"ace, rar and zip. Passwords can be stored in <application>KWallet</"
"application>. Please note that the archive support first needs to be "
"properly <link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">configured</link> in "
"Konfigurator. To open the archive, use &Enter; key, (double-)click or the "
"&Right; key. &krusader; supports also <emphasis role=\"bold\">hidden "
"archives</emphasis>, these are renamed archives with a *wrong* extension, "
"&eg; <trademark class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark> uses zip "
"archives with the following extensions: <literal role=\"extension\">.odt</"
"literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.sxw</literal> and <literal role="
"\"extension\">.odw</literal>. &Enter; will open the <trademark class="
"\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark> document and the &Right; key will open "
"the archive. Another example is J2EE, where the <literal role=\"extension\">."
"jar</literal> extension means a zip archive. Since &krusader; auto-detects "
"the supported archive types, it will open with &Right; key even if it has "
"another &MIME; type. Please note that browsing archives has a few "
"limitations:"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Navidezni datotečni sistemi (VFS)</link> vam omogočajo "
"brskanje po arhivih, kot da bi šlo za mapo. Trenutno &krusader; podpira "
"naslednje vrste arhivov: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, "
"tar, xz, zip in 7-zip ter podpira naslednje arhive z geslom: arj, ace, rar "
"in zip. Gesla lahko shranite v <application>KWallet</application>. "
"Upoštevajte, da je treba podporo za arhive najprej pravilno <link linkend="
"\"konfig-archives\">konfigurirati</link> v Konfiguratorju. Če želite odpreti "
"arhiv, uporabite &Enter; tipko, (dvojni)klik ali &Right;. &krusader; podpira "
"tudi <emphasis role=\"bold\">skrite arhive</emphasis>, ti so preimenovani "
"arhivi z *napačno* končnico, &eg; <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">OpenOffice</trademark> uporablja arhive zip z naslednjimi končnicami: "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.odt</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">."
"sxw</literal> in <literal role=\"extension\">.odw</literal>. &Enter; bo "
"odprl dokument <trademark class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark> in "
"&Right; tipka bo odprla arhiv. Drug primer je J2EE, kjer končnica <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.jar</literal> pomeni arhiv zip. Ker je &krusader; "
"samodejno zazna podprte vrste arhivov, se odpre s tipko &Right;, tudi če ima "
"drugo &MIME; vrsto. Upoštevajte, da ima brskanje po arhivih nekaj omejitev:"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all functions are supported by all archive types. (&ie;: you can not "
"delete files in ace or rar archives)"
msgstr ""
"Vse vrste arhivov ne podpirajo vseh funkcij. (&ie;: ne morete brisati "
"datotek v arhivih ace ali rar)"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The permissions you have inside the archive are the same as the permissions "
"you have for the archive."
msgstr ""
"Dovoljenja, ki jih imate znotraj arhiva, so enaka dovoljenjem, ki jih imate "
"za arhiv."

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command line (if visible) will not follow you inside the archive but "
"will point to the archive folder."
msgstr ""
"Ukazna vrstica (če je vidna) vam ne bo sledila znotraj arhiva, ampak bo "
"kazala na arhivsko mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before any action is performed on files/folders inside the archive, they "
"must be extracted. The archive will be repacked when you leave it or when "
"&krusader; detects that extracted files have changed."
msgstr ""
"Preden se na datotekah/mapah znotraj arhiva izvede kakršno koli dejanje, jih "
"je treba ekstrahirati. Arhiv bo ponovno zapakiran, ko ga zapustite ali ko "
"&krusader; zazna, da so se ekstrahirane datoteke spremenile."

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Packing and un-packing are <quote>blocking operations</quote> that display a "
"progress dialog. However, this might change in the future since we are "
"planning to create more background operations."
msgstr ""
"Pakiranje in razpakiranje sta <quote>operaciji blokiranja</quote>, ki "
"prikažeta pogovorno okno napredka. Vendar se bo to v prihodnosti morda "
"spremenilo, saj načrtujemo ustvarjanje več operacij v ozadju."

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unpack Files"
msgstr "Razpakirajte datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are 2 ways to extract files from archives:"
msgstr "Obstajata dva načina za ekstrahiranje datotek iz arhivov:"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to unpack a whole archive(s), browse to the archive location, "
"select the archive(s) and select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Unpack</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo>. &krusader; will ask you where "
"to put the extracted files. The default location is the inactive panel "
"folder. If you do not cancel the operation, &krusader; will try to unpack "
"all the selected files in the inactive panel."
msgstr ""
"Če želite razpakirati celoten arhiv(e), poiščite lokacijo arhiva, izberite "
"arhiv(e) in izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razpakiraj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo>. &krusader; vas bo "
"vprašal, kam spraviti ekstrahirane datoteke. Privzeta lokacija je mapa "
"neaktivne plošče. Če operacije ne prekličete, &krusader; bo poskušal "
"razpakirati vse izbrane datoteke v neaktivni plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you only want to extract a part of the archive, then <link linkend="
"\"browsing-archives\">browse</link> the archive and copy the files you want "
"to extract to their new location just as you would copy <quote>normal</"
"quote> files. Note that unpacking from a browsed archive takes more time "
"(file by file unpack) compared to unpacking a whole archive with the first "
"method. The unpack operation can be put in a <link linkend=\"queue\">queue</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ekstrahirati samo del arhiva, potem <link linkend=\"browsing-"
"archives\">prebrskajte</link> arhiv in kopirajte datoteke, ki jih želite "
"ekstrahirati, na novo lokacijo, tako kot bi kopirali <quote> normalne</"
"quote> datoteke. Upoštevajte, da razpakiranje iz brskanega arhiva traja več "
"časa (razpakiranje datoteke za datoteko) v primerjavi z razpakiranjem "
"celotnega arhiva s prvo metodo. Operacijo razpakiranja lahko postavite v "
"<link linkend=\"queue\">čakalno vrsto</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packing Files"
msgstr "Pakiranje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to create a new archive, begin by selecting the elements you "
"want to pack in the active panel and select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pack...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>. A dialog will "
"pop-up prompting you to select the archive name and location. Select the "
"packer from one of the <link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">supported file name "
"extensions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov arhiv, začnite z izbiro elementov, ki jih želite "
"zapakirati, v aktivni plošči in izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pakiraj ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>. Pojavilo se bo "
"pogovorno okno, v katerem boste morali izbrati ime in lokacijo arhiva. "
"Izberite pakirnik iz ene od <link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">podprtih "
"pripon imen datotek</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add files to an existing archive(s), open the archive in one panel and "
"the files to be copied in the other panel, then simply copy the files into "
"the archive in exactly the same way you copy files into a <quote>normal</"
"quote> folder. The pack operation can be put in a <link linkend=\"queue"
"\">queue</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati datoteke v obstoječe arhive, odprite arhiv v eni plošči in "
"datoteke, ki jih želite kopirati, v drugi plošči, nato preprosto kopirajte "
"datoteke v arhiv na popolnoma enak način, kot kopirate datoteke v "
"<quote>normalno </quote> mapo. Operacijo pakiranja lahko postavite v <link "
"linkend=\"queue\">čakalno vrsto</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: archives.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Testing Archives"
msgstr "Arhiv testiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: archives.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; will not handle corrupted archives since it may result in data "
"loss. If you receive an error message when opening an archive, or if you "
"suspect that there is something wrong with the archive, you should test it "
"before use. To test an archive, browse (navigate) to the archive location "
"and select the archive. Next select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Test Archive</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>. &krusader; will test the "
"archive file and inform you whether the archive passed or failed the file "
"integrity test."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; ne bo obravnaval poškodovanih arhivov, ker lahko povzroči izgubo "
"podatkov. Če pri odpiranju arhiva prejmete sporočilo o napaki ali če sumite, "
"da je z arhivom kaj narobe, ga pred uporabo preizkusite. Če želite "
"preizkusiti arhiv, pobrskajte (pomaknite se) do lokacije arhiva in izberite "
"arhiv. Nato izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preizkusni arhiv</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>. &krusader; bo "
"preizkusil arhivsko datoteko in vas obvestil, ali je arhiv uspešno prestal "
"test celovitosti datoteke ali ne."
